version_description:
- We fixed the Mr.Dog stickers last time, however, super bug came on the first 5 packs, which some old devices couldn't load the packs. It's due to different image loader api we had used, which loads perfectly on 'png', but fails on 'gif' for some old devices. But no worry, our programmer has fixed every thing!~

- We're working really hard on the 7th pack, will announce you the 7th pack details on the next update~
